{"tid":1539583,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：修例的初心是正確的","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:14:59.000Z","uid":35063,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"645e6a880c99ae2e31f86a211601fc4eb091c4d1","tid":1539583,"uid":35063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"幫大家溫故知新，屌你老母你個初心呢，點對得住支持你既人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，林鄭的一直用字是「暫緩」，但並非如示威者所要求的「撤回」草案。她強調，堅持初心，若果「撤回」會令社會收到訊息條例沒有立足之地，因此決定暫緩再溝通。她又說到，修例的初心是正確的，但承認是解說工作做得不足。<br />\n<br />\nsoure:<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%2F&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcasbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=08af8ca6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%2F&h=a30f01f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"be6d56a95ee0f5ed524adcbc69017ba5